  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Starts at JOURNEY 0.48 — you are already halfway between familiar and alien, and the Climax threshold at 0.78 is reachable but not immediate. A triangle-wave pad breathing slowly with Tidal Pulse; hold a note and push into aftertouch and the shimmer begins its 1.5-second bloom. This is the anticipatory patch — the intake of breath before something irreversible.",
